rm%20A%20Star%20Capital%20to%20take%20Waymos%20only.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHartz%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20believes%20Waymo%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bleast%20expensive%20option.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20investor%20at%20A%20Star%20roughly%20estimated%20spending%20about%20%2410K%20on%20Waymos%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-vc-firms-funding-creator-economy-startups-next-phase-2024-6%23a-star-has-been-investing-in-ai-powered-tools-that-help-creators-make-content-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKevin%20Hartz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20early%20Uber%20angel%20investor%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Eventbrite%2C%20directed%20his%20San%20Francisco-based%20venture%20capital%20firm%2C%20A%20Star%20Capital%2C%20to%20only%20take%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaymo%20robotaxis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20because%20he%20believes%20they%20provide%20the%20best%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWaymo%20is%20now%20required%20in%20SF%20as%20it%20is%20always%20substantially%20lower%20price%20and%20often%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartz%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20his%20firm%20of%2010%20employees%20on%20January%2016%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20on%20X.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20VC%20head%20wrote%20that%20a%20ride%20in%20an%20Uber%20%26quot%3BGreen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20sustainable%20ride%20option%20offered%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20was%20%2450%20to%20his%20destination%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20whereas%20a%20ride%20back%20with%20a%20Waymo%2C%20which%20only%20operates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-jaguar-all-electric-self-driving-cars-i-pace-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJaguar%20I-PACE%3C%2Fa%3E%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20was%20%2419.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartz%20told%20Business%20Insider%20over%20the%20phone%20that%20his%20email%20was%20indeed%20a%20serious%20mandate%20g