Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Waymo%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20study%20conducted%20last%20year%20by%20Evercore%20ISI%2C%20comparing%201%2C000%20trips%20across%20the%20Waymo%2C%20Uber%2C%20and%20Lyft%20platforms%2C%20analysts%20found%20that%20Waymo's%20pricing%20has%20become%20increasingly%20competitive%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20a%20Waymo%20ride%20for%20that%20quarter%20was%20%2421.91%2C%20compared%20to%20%2421.34%20for%20an%20UberX%20%E2%80%94%20the%20basic%20level%20of%20service%20the%20rideshare%20platform%20offers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20%2422.36%20for%20a%20Lyft.%20Prices%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20exclude%20tips%20to%20drivers%2C%20Evercore%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20their%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Uber%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Lyft%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHartz%20said%20he%20was%20an%20early%20believer%20in%20Uber%2C%20participating%20in%20the%20company's%20series%20B%20funding%20round%20in%202011%20at%20a%20%24300-million%20valuation.%20He%20declined%20to%20disclose%20a%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20experience%20in%20Waymo%20has%20made%20him%20a%20convert%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20privacy%20the%20robotaxi%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20quiet%20place%20where%20you%20can%20kind%20of%20reflect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhushi%20Suri%2C%20an%20ex-investor%20at%20A%20Star%2C%20had%20already%20embraced%20Hartz's%20Waymo-only%20directive%20long%20before%20he%20shared%20his%20January%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20February%2020%2C%20Suri%20took%20547%20rides%2C%20traveled%201%2C680%20miles%2C%20and%20spent%2010%2C005%20minutes%20inside%20a%20Waymo%2C%20she%20told%20BI.%20She%20roughly%20estimated%20spending%20%2410%2C000%20on%20Waymo%20rides%20in%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20the%20way%20there%2C%20I%20was%20enchanted%2C%26quot%3B%20Suri%20told%20BI%20of%20her%20first%20Waymo%20ride.%20%26quot%3BBut%20on%20the%20ride%20back%2C%20I%20forgot.%20It's%20just%20so%20natural.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuri%20said%20she%20was%20a%20heavy%20Uber%20user%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bresented%20it.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20the%20privacy%20of%20a%20Waymo%20allows%20her%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20when%20she%20and%20her%20friends%20are%20going%20out%20and%20dressed%20for%20clubbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Waymo%2C%20there's%20no%20walk%20of%20shame%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20intimate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20and%20Lyft%20had%20originally%20pursued%20an%20in-house%20autonomous%20vehicle%20program%20before%20selling%20them%20off%20in%202020%20and%202021%2C%20respectively.%20Both%20rideshare%20platforms%20are%20pursuing%20partnerships%20with%20other%20autonomous%20vehicle%20companies%20to%20offer%20a%20robotaxi%20service%2C%20leveraging%20its%20existing%20user%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUber%20plans%20to%20deepen%20its%20existing%20partnership%20with%20the%20Alphabet-owned%20company%20by%20managing%20a%20Waymo%20fleet%20in%20Austin%20and%20Atlanta%20sometime%20in%202025.%20The%20company%20already%20offers%20Waymos%20in%20Phoenix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20very%20happy%20that%20Uber%20had%20discontinued%20their%20self-driving%20program%2C%26quot%3B%20Hartz%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20glad%20that%20they're%20partnering%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-uber-angel-investor-kevin-hartz-vc-a-star-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740646802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bf758ab8b41a9673f9142e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-uber-angel-investor-kevin-hartz-vc-a-star-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Eventbrite%20CEO%20Kevin%20Hartz%20told%20his%20employees%20at%20A%20Star%20Capital%20that%20they%20should%20take%20Waymos%20only%20because%20they%20provide%20better%20value.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-uber-angel-investor-kevin-hartz-vc-a-star-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Marital%20conflicts%2C%20financial%20losses%2C%20and%20lawsuits'%3A%20Crypto-addiction%20therapists%20dish%20on%20the%20havoc%20it%20creates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22crypto%20trading%20addiction%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67be45dde015c5d98a6aec44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Elixu%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDemand%20for%20crypto-trading%20addiction%20therapy%20is%20rising%2C%20experts%20in%20the%20space%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECrypto%20addiction%20mirrors%20gambling%20addiction%2C%20driven%20by%20excitement%20and%20potential%20financial%20gain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETherapists%20note%20clients%20often%20face%20legal%20issues%2C%20financial%20losses%2C%20and%20personal%20life%20disruptions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENavigating%20the%20notoriously%20volatile%20crypto%20market%20is%20an%20exceedingly%20difficult%20thing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-gains-lock-in-avoid-crash-dogecoin-millionaire-bitcoin-price-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebitcoin%20coming%20off%20a%20124%25%20rally%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmemecoins-cryptocurrency-altcoins-market-trump-libra-milei-celebrities-scams-regulation-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememe%20coins%3C%2Fa%3E%20surge%20in%20popularity%2C%20some%20can't%20see%20the%20excessive%20risk%20that%20lies%20beyond%20what%20they%20deem%20a%20bevy%20of%20opportunities%20to%20strike%20it%20rich.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20eventually%2C%20it%20gets%20them%20into%20trouble%20%E2%80%94%20so%20much%20so%20that%20some%20conclude%20that%20they%20need%20to%20seek%20professional%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20therapy%20and%20counseling%20firms%20now%20offer%20crypto-related%20services%2C%20which%20have%20become%20more%20popular%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20according%20to%20professionals%20in%20the%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20asked%20two%20therapists%20about%20their%20experiences%20with%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20below%20are%20some%20of%20their%20top%20observations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22698149e8-ddff-4dc9-8faf-5e9fdbd041f9%5C%22%3ECrypto%20addiction%20often%20resembles%20gambling%20addiction%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20cryptocurrencies%20are%20relatively%20new%2C%20experts%20say%20the%20characteristics%20exemplified%20by%20traders%20who%20have%20gotten%20to%20the%20point%20of%20addiction%20often%20resemble%20those%20of%20an%20older%20condition%3A%20gambling%20addiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20odds%20of%20winning%20aren't%20always%20even.%20Nor%20are%20they%20as%20transparent%20as%20they%20are%20in%2C%20say%2C%20casino%20games%20or%20sports%20gambling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20quick%20way%20to%20make%20money%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20it's%20a%20skill-based%20form%20of%20gambling%2C%20and%20there%20are%20certainly%20more%20losers%20than%20winners%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Craig%20Bilton%2C%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3Eclinical%20director%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiamondrehabthailand.com%2Fwhat-is-crypto-addiction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Diamond%20Rehab%20Thailand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20rehab%20center%20with%20a%20one-month%20minimum%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20gambling%20addictions%2C%20the%20dopamine%20from%20the%20first%20win%20keeps%20people%20coming%20back.%20But%20oftentimes%2C%20like%20with%20gambling%2C%20it's%20not%20even%20about%20making%20money%20itself%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20about%20the%20excitement%20of%20taking%20on%20the%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20work%20on%20the%20same%20circuit%20of%20the%20brain%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilton%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20an%20initial%20win%20that%20creates%20the%20hook.%20And%20then%20after%20that%2C%20it's%20the%20anticipation%20of%20the%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f99e46d8-fb95-4dda-a423-00b51408f842%5C%22%3EClients%20sometimes%20miss%20their%20sessions%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20repercussions%20for%20crimes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBobbe%20McGinley%2C%20clinical%20director%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbircheshealth.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBirches%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20that%20some%20clients%20are%20likely%20involved%20in%20illegal%20activity%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20absence%20from%20therapy%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCryptocurrency%20frauds%20and%20scams%2C%20ranging%20from%20phishing%2C%20Ponzi%20schemes%20and%20pyramid%20schemes%2C%20to%20market%20manipulation%2C%20have%20been%20growing%20in%20frequency%20and%20magnitude%20over%20the%20past%20years%2C%20inflicting%20considerable%20financial%20losses%20on%20victims%2C%20and%20becoming%20an%20issue%20of%20significant%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20McGinley%20said%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndividuals%20involved%20often%20do%20not%20report%20for%20therapy%2C%20support%2C%20and%20assistance%20due%20to%20the%20complexity%20of%20their%20shame%2C%20and%20stress%20and%20anxiety%20about%20potential%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ce4f73fa-03c0-413e-8812-caef1e81f3cf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EClients%20have%20usually%20suffered%20big%20financial%20losses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20recently%20had%20a%20client%20that%20lost%20half%20a%20million%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sums%20of%20money%20aren't%20always%20that%20big%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20amounts%20are%20usually%20significant%20relative%20to%20each%20trader%2C%20according%20to%20Bilton.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20take%20a%20cocaine%20addict%2C%20the%20cocaine%20addict%20will%20stop%20using%20when%20they%20run%20out%20of%20cocaine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20gambling%20addict%20or%20a%20cryptocurrency%20or%20day-trading%20addict%2C%20they%20stop%20using%20when%20they've%20run%20out%20of%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22338ac6fe-a499-45bf-af4e-d04a0abe9dc5%5C%22%3EThe%20addiction%20is%20the%20symptom%20of%20another%20underlying%20issue%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20always%20be%20able%20to%20go%20deeper.%20We%20always%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20figure%20out%3A%20why%20the%20behavior%2C%20why%20the%20pain%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilton%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20is%20the%20addiction%20meets%20legitimate%20needs%2C%20but%20in%20an%20illegitimate%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231e87b56-652f-45c7-89a8-d7f8e683d370%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrypto-trading%20addictions%20often%20harm%20many%20parts%20of%20clients'%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20financial%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20individuals%20often%20spend%20considerable%20amounts%20of%20time%20daily%20on%20trading%20activities%20(neglecting%20other%20areas%20of%20their%20lives)%20and%20highly%20value%20social%20status%20and%20success%2C%20being%20highly%20competitive%2C%26quot%3B%20McGinley%20said.%20%26quot%3BReported%20negative%20consequences%20are%20not%20rare%20and%20can%20be%20varied%3A%20from%20marital%20conflicts%2C%20financial%20losses%20and%20lawsuits%20to%20adverse%20psychological%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBilton%20said%20he's%20seen%20similar%20issues%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp