for%20medical%20emergencies%20are%20normally%20given%20quickly.%20It%20is%20unclear%20what%20led%20to%20the%20delay%20in%20this%20instance.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Shinde%20-%20a%20student%20at%20California%20State%20University%20-%20suffered%20serious%20injuries%2C%20including%20fractures%2C%20after%20she%20was%20mowed%20down%20from%20behind%20by%20a%20four-wheeler%20on%20February%2014.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHer%20family%20applied%20for%20a%20visa%2048%20hours%20later%2C%20but%20the%20application%20has%20been%20pending%20since.%20Ms%20Shinde's%20uncle%2C%20Kadam%20Shinde%2C%20told%20NDTV%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffamily-of-comatose-indian-student-nilam-shinde-in-us-getting-visa-slot-for-2026-7806173%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearliest%20available%20date%20is%20for%20next%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMs%20Shinde's%20family%20said%20the%20crash%20left%20her%20with%20fractures%20in%20both%20arms%20and%20both%20legs%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finjures-on-head-chest-indian-student-nilam-shindes-medical-condition-after-us-crash-7805784%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequired%20emergency%20brain%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20which%20consent%20had%20been%20sought%20from%20the%20hospital%20administration.%20The%20young%20woman%20has%20been%20in%20a%20coma%20since%20the%20surgery%2C%20reports%20indicate.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20statement%20from%20the%20university%20-%20issued%20February%2016%20-%20said%20Ms%20Shinde%20%26quot%3Bis%20in%20critical%20condition%20with%20an%20uncertain%20prognosis%20and%20is%20receiving%20care%20in%20the%20Intensive%20Care%20Unit%26quot%3B.%20The%20university%20added%20its%20appeal%20for%20travel%20permits%20to%20be%20issued%20for%20the%20family.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20patient's%20father%20must%20assist%20the%20UC%20Davis%20Medical%20Centre%20care%20team%20with%20making%20Ms%20Shinde's%20medical%20care%20plan