94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1894973695992701437%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EGade%20has%20now%20been%20on%20the%20run%20for%20over%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'News%20Was%20Suppressed%20Because...'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJunior%20Home%20Minister%20Yogesh%20Kadam%20this%20morning%20said%20that%20although%20the%20woman%20had%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint%2C%20the%20press%20had%20not%20been%20informed%20to%20ensure%20the%20accused%20was%20not%20alerted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20complaint%20was%20received%2C%20and%20police%20started%20a%20search%20within%20half%20an%20hour.%20But%20the%20news%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20come%20out...%20this%20was%20so%20the%20accused%20would%20not%20be%20alerted%20and%20try%20to%20escape.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kadam%20also%20said%20his%20office%20had%20checked%20the%20number%20of%20times%20police%20had%20patrolled%20the%20crime%20scene%20in%20the%20hours%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20rape.%20%26quot%3BPatrolling%20was%20at%201%20am%20and%203%20am...%20officer%20had%20come%20and%20gone%20two%20times%20before%20the%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20have%20taken%20all%20necessary%20steps...%20we%20have%20checked%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20and%20the%20accused%20has%20been%20identified.%20We%20are%20tracking%20the%20accused...%20his%20probable%20location%20has%20been%20found.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPune%20Bus%20Stand%20Rape%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rape%20took%20place%20between%205.45%20am%20and%206%20am%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20woman%2C%20a%20domestic%2C%20was%20waiting%20to%20board%20a%20bus%20to%20her%20hometown%20in%20Satara%20district%20when%20she%20was%20accosted%20by%20Gade%2C%20who%2C%20she%20told%20the%20cops%2C%20addressed%20her%20as%20'%3Cem%3Edidi%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20'sister'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Gade%20inquired%20after%20her%20destination%20and%20persuaded%20her%20that%20a%20bus%20parked%20in%20one%20corner%20of%20the%20busy%20depot%20would%20take%20her%20there.%20CCTV%20footage%20showed%20the%20two%20walking%20to%20that%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FOut%2520On%2520Bail%2C%2520Man%2520Rapes%2520Pune%2520Woman%2520Inside%2520Bus%2520100%2520Metres%2520From%2520Police%2520Station%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPune%20Woman%20Raped%20In%20Bus%20By%20Man%20On%20Bail%20Since%202019%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20bus%20-%20which%20had%20no%20lights%20on%20-%20the%20woman%20said%20she%20hesitated%20but%20was%20told%20that%20was%20because%20other%20passengers%20on%20board%20were%20asleep.%20She%20was%20encouraged%20to%20enter%20the%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20the%20cops%20Gade%20jumped%20in%20after%20her%2C%20locked%20the%20door%2C%20and%20raped%20her.%20After%20the%20assault%20Gade%20slunk%20away%20and%20the%20woman%20told%20a%20friend%2C%20who%20convinced%20her%20to%20file%20a%20police%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20they%20had%20equally%20immediately%20filed%20a%20complaint%20and%20accessed%20the%20CCTV%20footage%2C%20which%20jumpstarted%20their%20investigation%2C%20which%20will%20include%20inquiries%20into%20how%20and%20why%20the%20bus%20depot%20management%20allowed%20this%20to%20happen%20in%20their%20premises%20and%20on%20their%20bus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-woman-raped-in-middle-of-bus-stand-near-police-station-7799785%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPune%20Woman%20Raped%20In%20Bus%20Parked%20100%20Metres%20From%20Police%20Station%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20State%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation%20-%20under%20fire%20for%20poor%20security%20-%20has%20replaced%20guards%20at%20the%20depot%20and%20announced%20an%20inquiry%20of%20its%20own%2C%20with%20a%20report%20to%20be%20filed%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MSRTC%20is%20one%20of%20the%20three%20public%20transport%20bodies%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%20fleet%20of%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20buses.%20Every%20day%2C%20more%20than%2055%20lakh%20passengers%20travel%20on%20its%20buses%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20horrific%20incident%20has%20triggered%20a%20predictable%20political%20row%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20gunning%20for%20the%20ruling%20Mahayuti%20combine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20Congress%20unit%20chief%2C%20Harshwardhan%20Sapkal%2C%20slammed%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20the%20state%20for%20focusing%20on%20'freebies'%20for%20women%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20their%20safety%2C%20and%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20from%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar-led%20NCP%20faction%2C%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20not%20being%20able%20to%20ensure%20women's%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Maharashtra%20%7C%20Leaders%20and%20party%20workers%20of%20NCP-SCP%20staged%20a%20protest%20outside%20Swargate%20police%20station%20against%20the%20Pune%20Swargate%20bus%20depot%20rape%20incident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYMclZ8OtQY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYMclZ8OtQY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1894978038510792818%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20has%20vowed%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20the%20woman%2C%20with%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20calling%20the%2