%3BIt%20is%20only%20Sanskrit%20that%20is%20prioritised%20under%20the%20three-language%20policy%20in%20most%20states...%20but%20Tamil%20is%20protected%20by%20the%20Dravidian%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20then%20declared%20that%20Sanskrit%20teachers%20had%20replaced%20Urdu%20counterparts%20in%20Rajasthan%20schools.%20%26quot%3B...%20should%20ask%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi%20how%20many%20boards%20in%20south%20Indian%20languages%20were%20put%20up%20during%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20and%20Tamil%20Sangamam%20(in%20Varanasi)%20...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindi%20is%20not%20UP's%20mother%20tongue...%20UP%20lost%20Bhojpuri%2C%20Bundelkhandi%20(or%20Bundeli).%20Uttarakhand%20lost%20Kumaoni.%20Native%20languages%20were%20lost%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Chattisgarh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETamil%20Nadu%20vs%20Centre%20In%20'Language%20War'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin's%20sharp%20jabs%20underline%20the%20friction%20between%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20other%20southern%20states%2C%20and%20the%20centre%20over%20the%20three-language%20push%20in%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20-%20which%20has%20always%20been%20suspicious%20of%20'Hindi%20imposition'%20-%20has%20had%20a%20two-language%20policy%20since%201967%2C%20when%20efforts%20by%20the%20then-Congress-led%20centre%20to%20make%20Hindi%20the%20'official%20language'%20triggered%20violent%20riots%2C%20and%20led%20to%20the%20national%20party%20losing%20power%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20latest%20round%20of%20protests%20flared%20up%20after%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20said%20he%20will%20withhold%20Rs%202%2C400%20crore%20in%20funds%20for%20Tamil%20Nadu%20if%20it%20does%20not%20fully%20implement%20the%20new%20education%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20and%20his%20son%2C%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Udhayanidhi%20Sta