20generational%2C%20and%20ideological%20divisions%E2%80%94west%20Germany%20largely%20stayed%20with%20the%20CDU%2C%20while%20the%20east%20overwhelmingly%20backed%20AfD.%20As%20the%20political%20establishment%20scrambles%20to%20form%20a%20governing%20coalition%2C%20questions%20arise%20over%20Germany's%20future%20direction%2C%20especially%20in%20security%2C%20economic%20policy%2C%20and%20its%20place%20in%20the%20European%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20domestic%20concerns%2C%20the%20election%20comes%20at%20a%20critical%20geopolitical%20moment%2C%20with%20Germany's%20foreign%20policy%2C%20relations%20with%20the%20U.S.%2C%20and%20its%20role%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20under%20scrutiny.%20The%20war%20has%20strained%20Germany's%20economy%20and%20security%20posture%2C%20while%20debates%20over%20NATO's%20future%20and%20European%20defense%20autonomy%20signal%20unease%20in%20Berlin's%20policy%20circles.%20CDU%20leader%20Friedrich%20Merz%2C%20the%20likely%20next%20chancellor%2C%20will%20shape%20Germany's%20stance%20on%20Ukraine%20aid%2C%20European%20security%2C%20and%20transatlantic%20ties.%20These%20issues%20will%20dominate%20coalition%20negotiations%20and%20Germany's%20policy%20realignment%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Grand%20Coalition%20Is%20Likely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20election%20results%20reflect%20a%20growing%20generational%20realignment%20in%20German%20politics.%20CDU%20retained%20strong%20support%20among%20older%20voters%2C%20especially%20those%20above%2060%2C%20where%20it%20secured%20over%2040%25%20of%20the%20vote.%20However%2C%20among%20the%20youth%2C%20CDU%20lost%20ground%20to%20AfD%2C%20which%20gained%20remarkable%20traction%20among%20voters%20aged%2018-34.%20The%20Social%20Democratic%20Party%20(SPD)%20suffered%20a%20significant%20decline%2C%20as%20younger%20left-wing%20voters%20shifted%20to%20Die%20Linke%20and%20the%20newly%20formed%20Sahra%20Wagenknecht%20Alliance%20(BSW).%20The%20Free%20Democratic%20Party%20(FDP)%20collapsed%20below%20the%20electoral%20threshold%2C%20indicating%20the%20waning%20appeal%20of%20economic%20centrism%20among%20young%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20mainstream%20parties%20ruling%20out%20cooperation%20with%20AfD%2C%20a%20CDU-SPD%20%E2%80%98grand%20coalition'%20is%20the%20most%20viable%20option.%20Friedrich%20Merz%20(69)%20has%20set%20Easter%20as%20the%20deadline%20to%20finalise%20a%20coalition%20agreement%2C%20emphasising%20economic%20stability%2C%20European%20integration%2C%20and%20security%20concerns.%20The%20new%20Bundestag%20begins%20its%20term%20on%20March%2025.%20Merz%20aims%20to%20collaborate%20with%20the%20SPD%20and%20Greens%20on%20debt%20brakes%2C%20signaling%20his%20eagerness%20for%20a%20fresh%20start.%20Securing%20an%20agreement%20would%20be%20a%20major%20win%20for%20him.%20Despite%20its%20poor%20showing%2C%20SPD%20is%20likely%20to%20accept%20a%20junior%20role%20in%20government%2C%20though%20the%20Scholz%20faction%20may%20take%20a%20backseat%20due%20to%20electoral%20pragmatism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20coalition%20faces%20two%2C%20rather%20three%2C%20major%20challenges%3A%20economic%20recovery%2C%20defense%20and%20Ukraine.%20Germany's%20economic%20slowdown%2C%20exacerbated%20by%20inflation%2C%20energy%20dependency%2C%20and%20global%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%2C%20demands%20urgent%20action.%20With%20CDU's%20pro-business%20stance%2C%20the%20new%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20push%20for%20corporate%20tax%20reforms%2C%20deregulation%2C%20and%20incentives%20for%20skilled%20labour%20migration%E2%80%94an%20essential%20step%20as%20Germany%20faces%20severe%20labor%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerz%20seeks%20to%20prioritise%20achieving%20greater%20independence%20in%20foreign%20policy%20and%20defense%20matters%2C%20seeking%20a%20step-by-step%20reduction%20of%20reliance%20on%20the%20US%20while%20advancing%20European%20security%20autonomy.%20This%20shift%20will%20be%20closely%20watched%20by%20NATO%20allies%20and%20EU%20partners%2C%20as%20it%20reflects%20Germany's%20attempt%20to%20balance%20transatlantic%20commitments%20with%20a%20more%20self-reliant%20European%20defense%20strategy.%20Friedrich%20Merz%20has%20also%20pledged%20continued%20support%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20as%20against%20President%20Trump%2C%20reinforcing%20Germany's%20role%20in%20European%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS-Russia%20Manoeuvring%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20debates%20occur%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20recent%20geopolitical%20manoeuvers%E2%80%94most%20notably%20the%20Riyadh%20meeting%20between%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20Putin's%20representatives%2C%20which%20has%20alarmed%20European%20allies%20over%20a%20potential%20US-Russia%20understanding%20that%20bypasses%20Ukraine.%20In%20response%2C%20European%20leaders%20convened%20in%20Paris%20to%20discuss%20forming%20a%20European%20peacekeeping%20force%2C%20seeking%20greater%20autonomy%20in%20regional%20security%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20another%20European%20summit%20planned%20for%20early%20March%2C%20further%20steps%20toward%20a%20coordinated%20EU%20security%20strategy%20on%20Ukraine%20will%20be%20debated.%20Meanwhile%2C%20at%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%2C%20US%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20signalled%20a%20more%20restrained%20American%20role%20in%20European%20security%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20need%20for%20Germany%20and%20the%20EU%20to%20reassess%20their%20defense%20commitments%20amid%20shifting%20transatlantic%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Warning%20to%20the%20Establishment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfD's%20historic%20gains%20in%20eastern%20Germany%20highlight%20widespread%20frustration%20with%20economic%20stagnation%2C%20migration%20policies%2C%20and%20political%20elites.%20The%20party's%20success%20among%20undecided%20voters%20indicates%20that%20many%20Germans%20feel%20disconnected%20from%20mainstream%20politics.%20AfD's%20new%20role%20as%20the%20largest%20opposition%20party%20means%20it%20will%20push%20hardline%20anti-immigration%20measures%20and%20challenge%20EU%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20CDU%20and%20SPD%2C%20AfD's%20rise%20presents%20a%20political%20dilemma.%20Ignoring%20the%20economic%20anxiety%2C%20cultural%20tensions%2C%20and%20security%20fears%20fuelling%20its%20rise%20will%20only%20push%20more%20voters%20toward%20them.%20But%20directly%20engaging%20with%20AfD's%20rhetoric%20risks%20legitimising%20its%20positions%20and%20shifting%20German%20politics%20further%20to%20the%20right.%20The%20coalition%20government%20must%20tackle%20public%20concerns%20head-on%20without%20normalising%20populism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20On%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20election%20results%20come%20at%20a%20critical%20juncture%20for%20India-Germany%20and%20India-Europe%20relations.%20With%20top%20EU%20officials%20visiting%20New%20Delhi%20on%20February%2027-28%2C%20discussions%20will%20focus%20on%20skilled%20labour%20migration%2C%20trade%20agreements%2C%20and%20strategic%20cooperation.%20Germany%2C%20facing%20a%20workforce%20shortage%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20push%20for%20relaxed%20migration%20policies%2C%20making%20India%20a%20key%20partner%20in%20supplying%20skilled%20labour%2C%20particularly%20in%20IT%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20strategic%20standpoint%2C%20India%20will%20closely%20monitor%20Germany's%20evolving%20stance%20on%20China%2C%20defence%2C%20and%20transatlantic%20relations.%20While%20Merz%20has%20reaffirmed%20support%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20his%20push%20for%20European%20defense%20autonomy%20signals%20a%20potential%20shift%20in%20Berlin's%20foreign%20policy%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Merz%20has%20expressed%20a%20favourable%20outlook%20toward%20strengthening%20relations%20with%20India.%20In%202024%2C%20meeting%20with%20Indian%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr.%20S.%20Jaishankar%20in%20Berlin%2C%20Merz%20and%20C