arget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskyrocketing%20price%20of%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20McDonald's%20is%20going%20the%20other%20way%20and%20selling%20%241%20Egg%20McMuffins%20for%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20McDonald's%20announced%20it%20will%20be%20selling%20Egg%20McMuffins%20and%20Sausage%20McMuffins%20with%20Egg%20for%20%241%20on%20Sunday%2C%20March%202.%20The%20deal%20is%20only%20valid%20for%20purchases%20made%20through%20the%20app%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20promotion%20is%20being%20held%20to%20celebrate%20the%20Egg%20McMuffin's%2050th%20birthday.%20The%20product%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20US%20in%201975.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20menu%20prices%20vary%20depending%20on%20location.%20In%20downtown%20Manhattan%2C%20an%20Egg%20McMuffin%20currently%20costs%20%245.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20North%20America%20impact%20officer%2C%20Michael%20Gonda%2C%20wrote%20a%20LinkedIn%20post%20on%20Tuesday%20about%20the%20deal.%20Referencing%20egg%20prices%2C%20Gonda%20said%20customers%20%26quot%3Bdefinitely%20WON'T%20see%20McDonald's%20USA%20issuing%20surcharges%20on%20eggs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2261d01b1a-d800-458c-913c-f10b059d304e%5C%22%3EValue%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDipanjan%20Chatterjee%2C%20a%20vice%20president%20at%20Forrester%2C%20a%20New%20York-based%20market%20research%20company%2C%20told%20BI%20the%20deal%20fits%20right%20into%20McDonald's%20value%20strategy%2C%20which%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-bet-on-5-dollar-mcvalue-meals-paying-off-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%245%20meal%20deals%20and%20%241%20items.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatterjee%20said%20that%20with%20egg%20prices%20hitting%20all-time%20highs%2C%20marketing%20a%20%26quot%3B%241%20value%20item%26quot%3B%20that%20uses%20eggs%20%26quot%3Bmay%20seem%20like%20an%20odd%20choice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20more%20of%20an%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20b