profoundly%20anti-democratic%20actions%20of%20Musk.%20Angus%20said%20that%20Musk%20has%20said%20Canada%20is%20not%20a%20real%20country%20and%20that%20he%20is%20the%20right-hand%20man%20of%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20who%20doesn't%20believe%20Canada%20had%20a%20right%20to%20exist%20so%20Musk%20could%20pose%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20Canada's%20sovereignty.%20Angus%20was%20referring%20to%20a%20tweet%20by%20Elon%20Musk%20that%20said%20%26quot%3BCanada%20is%20not%20a%20real%20country%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20response%20to%20the%20petition%20but%20took%20down%20that%20tweet%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadian%20citizenship%20can%20only%20be%20revoked%20if%20a%20person%20has%20committed%20fraud%2C%20misrepresented%20themself%2C%20or%20knowingly%20hid%20information%20on%20an%20immigration%20or%20citizenship%20application.%20The%20Conservative%20government%20of%20Stephen%20Harper%20had%20introduced%20a%20bill%20C-24%20in%202015%20that%20sought%20revocation%20of%20citizenship%20for%20terror%2C%20treason%2C%20or%20espionage.%20It%20had%20been%20a%20topic%20of%20heated%20debate%20with%20the%20then-leader%20of%20the%20Liberal%20Party%20Justin%20Trudeau%20opposing%20any%20conditionality%20attached%20to%20citizenship%20saying%20it%20devalues%20it.%20Trudeau%20had%20argued%20that%20offences%20should%20be%20dealt%20with%20through%20appropriate%20laws%20and%20punishments%20rather%20than%20making%20citizenship%20itself%20conditional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20NDP%20MP%20Angus%20wrote%20to%20Election%20Canada%20seeking%20an%20investigation%20into%20Musk%20owned%2C%20X%20and%20how%20it%20could%20be%20used%20to%20manipulate%20the%20Canadian%20federal%20election.%20He%20asked%20the%20election%20body%20to%20extract%20a%20commitment%20from%20Musk%20on%20the%20algorithmic%20transparency%20that%20would%20allow%20election%20observers%20to%20see%20whether%20X%20was%20interfering%20with%20the%20promotion%20or%20suppression%20of%20political%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publis