tion%20MPs%20on%20the%20panel%20said%20sections%20of%20their%20dissent%20notes%20had%20vanished%20from%20the%20submitted%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre%20denied%20the%20accusation%20but%20said%20the%20JPC%20boss%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP's%20Jagadambika%20Pal%2C%20had%20the%20discretion%20to%20remove%20sections%20casting%20'aspersions'%20on%20the%20committee.%20However%2C%20following%20a%20meeting%20between%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Kiren%20Rijiju%2C%20and%20protesting%20opposition%20MPs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-vs-opposition-over-dissent-notes-in-house-panel-report-on-waqf-bill-7699890%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20was%20decided%20the%20dissent%20notes%20would%20be%20included%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20original%20(and%20entire)%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-joint-parliamentary-committee-mockery-opposition-mps-in-waqf-house-panel-say-their-suggestions-ignored-7585859%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpposition%20MPs%20In%20Waqf%20House%20Panel%20Say%20Their%20Suggestions%20Ignored%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubmission%20of%20the%20JPC's%20report%20was%20after%20a%20prolonged%20fight%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20committee's%20functioning%2C%20with%20Mr%20Pal%20accused%20of%20bias%20and%20rushing%20the%20bill%20without%20proper%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20MPs%20had%20written%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20accused%C2%A0Mr%20Pal%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bsteamroll%26quot%3B%20the%20Waqf%20Bill%20through%20the%20House%20with%20one%20eye%20on%20the%20February%205%20Delhi%20election%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconduct-proceedings-in-fair-transparent-manner-suspended-opposition-mps-write-to-speaker-after-waqf-panel-meet-7550302%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEnsure%20Fair%20Proceedings%26quot%3B%3A%20Suspended%20Waqf%20Panel%20MPs%20To%20Speaker%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20though%2C%20had%20refuted%20those%20claims%3B%20panel%20member%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20Aparajita%20Sarangi%20said%C2%A0Mr%20Pal%20%26quot%3Btried%20to%20hear%20everybody%20out%20and%20gave%20sufficient%20time%20for%20everybody%20to%20move%20amendments...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JPC%20did%20hold%20nearly%20three%20dozen%20hearings%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months%20but%20many%20of%20those%20ended%20in%20chaos%2C%20and%20at%20least%20one%20in%20physical%20violence%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-joint-parliamentary-committee-kalyan-banerjee-trinamools-kalyan-banerjee-explains-hulk-moment-during-waqf-bill-meeting-6899719%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20MP%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20smashed%20a%20glass%20bottle%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20table%2C%20after%20claiming%20provocation%20from%20the%20BJP's%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2066%20changes%20were%20proposed%2C%20of%20which%20all%2044%20from%20the%20opposition%20were%20rejected%2C%20triggering%20another%20spat.%20The%2023%20from%20BJP%20and%20allied%20parties%20were%20accepted%20and%2C%20after%20a%20vote%2C%2014%20were%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JPC%20had%2016%20MPs%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20allied%20parties%2C%20and%20only%2010%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EJPC%20Changes%20To%20Waqf%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2014%20alternations%20include%20distinguishing%20between%20the%20mandatory%20two%20non-Muslim%20members%20-%20as%20specified%20in%20the%20original%20draft%20of%20the%20bill%20-%20and%20nominated%20ex-officio%20members%20(Muslim%20or%20non-Muslim).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20waqf%20councils%2C%20whether%20at%20state%20or%20pan-India%20levels%2C%20will%20have%20at%20least%20two%2C%20and%20possibly%20more%20(if%20the%20nominated%20ex-officio%20members%20are%20also%20not%20Muslim)%20members%20not%20from%20the%20Islamic%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-amendment-bill-non-muslim-members-rules-on-2-non-muslim-members-among-14-changes-to-waqf-amendment-bill-7570160%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3ERules%20On%202%20Non-Muslims%20Among%2014%20Changes%20To%20Waqf%20Bill%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20change%20is%20directing%20an%20officer%20nominated%20by%20the%20concerned%20state%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20property%20is%20'waqf'.%20In%20the%20original%20draft%20this%20decision%20was%20left%20to%20the%20District%20Collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20is%20establishing%20that%20the%20law%20will%20not%20apply%20retrospectively%2C%20so%20long%20as%20the%20property%20in%20question%20is%20already%20registered.%20To%20this%20point%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20JPC%20member%20Imran%20Masood%20raised%20a%20red%20flag%2C%20noting%20an%20estimated%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20waqf%20properties%20are%20not%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Waqf%20Bill%20Had%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%2044%20changes%20in%20the%20draft%20bill%3B%20these%20were%20to%20rules%20governing%20central%20and%20state%20Waqf%20boards%2C%20which%20decide%20how%20Muslim%20charitable%20properties%20are%20managed%20in%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20proposals%20-%20which%20include%20nominating%20non-Muslim%20and%20(at%20least%20two)%20women%20members%20to%20every%20Waqf%20Board%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20Union%20Minister%2C%20three%20MPs%2C%20and%20four%20people%20of%20'national%20repute'%20to%20the%20central%20Waqf%20Council%20-%20had%20triggered%20furious%20protests%20from%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%20Explains%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwaqf-act-amendment-explainer-women-non-muslims-on-boards-council-cant-claim-land-waqf-act-changes-6282656%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWomen%2C%20Non-Muslims%2C%20Council%20Can't%20Claim%20Land%3A%20Waqf%20Changes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20proposed%20change%20was%20to%20limit%20donations%20from%20Muslims%20who%20must%20have%20been%20practicing%20for%20at%20least%20five%20years%20-%20a%20provision%20that%20triggered%20a%20row%20over%20the%20term%20'practicing%20Muslim'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20was%20to%20direct%20an%20officer%20nominated%20by%20the%20concerned%20state%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20property%20is%20'waqf'.%20In%20the%20original%20draft%20this%20decision%20was%20left%20to%20the%20District%20Collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20under%20the%20new%20rules%20the%20Waqf%20Council%20could%20not%20claim%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20vs%20Opposition%20On%20Waqf%20Bill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20NDTV%20last%20year%20the%20idea%20is%20to%20empower%20Muslim%20women%20and%20children%20who%20had%20%26quot%3Bsuffered%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20old%20law.%20However%2C%20critics%2C%20including%20opposition%20leaders%20like%20the%20Congress'%20KC%20Venugopal%2C%20have%20said%20it%20constitutes%20a%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20attack%20on%20freedom%20of%20religion%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20bill's%20fiercest%20critics%2C%20and%20the%20DMK's%20Kanimozhi%20have%20also%20spoken%20out%2C%20arguing%20it%20violates%20multiple%20sections%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20including%20Article%2015%20(the%20right%20to%20practice%20a%20religion%20of%20one's%20choice)%20and%20Article%2030%20(the%20right%20to%20minority%20communities%20to%20establish%20and%20administer%20their%20e