d%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bwell-planned%20conspiracy%26quot%3B%20against%20Punjab%20and%20Punjabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%C2%A0said%20his%20department%20has%20issued%20a%20fresh%20notification%20stating%20that%20Punjabi%20will%20be%20a%20main%20subject%20in%20Class%2010%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20Punjabi%20is%20not%20a%20main%20subject%20in%20any%20school%2C%20then%20the%20certificate%20will%20be%20considered%20%26quot%3Bnull%20and%20void%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20will%20apply%20to%20all%20education%20boards%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftelangana-makes-telugu-compulsory-for-class-9-10-amid-tamil-nadu-hindi-imposition-row-7797269%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETelangana's%20Language%20Push%20Amid%20Tamil%20Nadu-Centre's%20'Hindi%20Imposition'%20Spat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bains%20said%20in%20the%20CBSE's%20draft%20norms%2C%20Science%2C%20Maths%2C%20Social%20Science%2C%20Hindi%20and%20English%20are%20the%20main%20subjects%20of%20Class%2010.%20The%20minister%20said%20that%20regional%20and%20foreign%20languages%20are%20in%20one%20group%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20subjects%20are%20in%20the%20other%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Punjabi%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20regional%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20Punjabi%20is%20not%20the%20main%20subject.%20The%20main%20regional%20language%20has%20been%20finished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%5BLive%5D%20Punjab%20School%20Education%20Minister%20Harjot%20Singh%20Bains%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20at%20Punjab%20Bhawan%2C%20Chd%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjcncFqntn8%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FjcncFqntn8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Government%20of%20Punjab%20(%40PbGovtIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPbGovtIndia%2Fstatus%2F1894714051395269037%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2026%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bains%20said%20that%20Punjabi%20is%20a%20well-spoken%20language%20in%20many%20states%2C%20including%20Haryana%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20West%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPunjabi%20is%20not%20just%20a%20language%3B%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20our%20rich%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20spoken%20and%20cherished%20by%20millions%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20current%20situation%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20erase%20Punjabi%20from%20the%20educational%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBSE's%20Clarification%20On%20Punjabi%20Subject%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20AAP%20minister's%20remarks%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbse-plans-to-conduct-class-10-board-exams-twice-a-year-7793709%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBSE%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20a%20clarification%20refuting%20his%20claims%20that%20Punjabi%20was%20removed%20from%20its%20list%20of%20regional%20language%20subjects%20for%20Class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clarified%20that%20the%20list%20of%20other%20subjects%20and%20languages%20contained%20in%20the%20draft%20date%20sheet%20is%20only%20indicative%20and%20that%20all%20the%20subjects%20and%20languages%20as%20offered%20presently%20shall%20continue%20to%20be%20offered%20for%202025-2026%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20CBSE%20Examination%20Controller%20Sanyam%20Bhardwaj%20said%20in%20an%20official%20notification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThus%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20languages%20mentioned%20under%20the%20list%20of%20languages%20in%20point%208%20of%20the%20draft%20policy%20under%20the%20heading%20%26quot%3BRegional%20and%20Foreign%20languages%20group%26quot%3B%2C%20Punjabi(004)%2C%20Russian(021)%2C%20Nepali(024)%2C%20Limboo(025)%2C%20Lepcha%20(026)%2C%20Sindhi(008)%2C%20Malayalam(012)%2C%20Odia(013)%2C%20Assamese(014)%2C%20Kannada(015)%2C%20Kokborok%20(091)%2C%20Telugu%20(007)%2C%20Arabic(016)%20and%20Persian(023)%20shall%20continue%20to%20be%20offered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECBSE's%20Draft%20Norms%20For%20Conducting%20Class%2010%20Board%20Exams%20Twice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20on%20Tuesday%20approved%20draft%20norms%20for%20conducting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcbses-dual-exam-proposal-for-class-10-check-important-faqs-7798409%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClass%2010%20board%20exams%3C%2Fa%3E%20twice%20a%20year.%20According%20to%20the%20draft%20norms%2C%20Class%2010%20students%20will%20be%20able%20to%20take%20the%20board%20exam%20twice%20in%20an%20academic%20session%20or%20choose%20between%20the%20two%20--%20one%20in%20February%20and%20another%20in%20May%20--%20from%202026%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20will%20be%20held%20from%20February%2017%20to%20March%206%2C%20while%20the%20second%20will%20be%20conducted%20between%20May%205%20and%2020.%20Candidates%20will%20also%20have%20the%20option%20to%20appear%20for%20both%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudents%20will%20also%20be%20allowed%20to%20skip%20specific%20subjects%20in%20the%20second%20attempt%20if%20they%20are%20satisfied%20with%20their%20performance%20in%20the%20first.%20They%20can%20skip%20particular%20subjects%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20recommended%20allowing%20all%20students%20to%20take%20exams%20on%20up%20to%20two%20occasions%20during%20any%20given%20school%20year%20to%20eliminate%20the%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20stakes%26quot%3B%20aspect%20of%20the%20board%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20has%20clarified%20that%20no%20separate%20supplementary%20exam%20would%20be%20conducted%20under%20this%20system.%20Instead%2C%20the%20second%20phase%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20supplementary%20exam%20for%20those%20students%20who%20want%20to%20improve%20their%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20norms%20will%20now%20be%20put%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20and%20the%20stakeholders%20can%20submit%20their%20feedback%20by%20March%209%20following%20which%20the%20policy%20will%20be%20finalised.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740628200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fbfnt3hgg_punjab-schools_625x300_27_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-minister-harjot-singh-bains-says-punjabi-dropped-from-list-of-subjects-for-class-10-board-exams-cbse-responds-7804545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Punjab%20Education%20Minister%20accused%20the%20CBSE%20of%20dropping%20Punjabi%20from%20the%20list%20of%20subjects%20for%20Class%2010%20in%20the%20new%20draft%20norms%20for%20biannual%20board%20exam%20format.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faap-minister-harjot-singh-bains-says-punjabi-dropped-from-list-of-subjects-for-class-10-board-exams-cbse-responds-7804545%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BBC%20Komla%20Dumor%20Award%202025%20launched%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740627939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3a1e%2Flive%2Fc5088320-f45d-11ef-8c03-7dfdbeeb2526.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc798d074wp2o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rising%20stars%20of%20African%20journalism%20are%20encouraged%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20award%2C%20which%20is%20now%20in%20its%2010th%20year.%22%2