%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223088%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22allison%20nichol%20longtin%20in%20her%20backyard%20with%20grass%20and%20her%20home%20behind%20her%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a613d447bbe40019834b06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221544%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Allison%20Nichol%20Longtin.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Nichol%20Longtin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20should've%20known%20better%20than%20to%20travel%20during%20the%20holidays%2C%20and%20I%20paid%20the%20cost%20for%20doing%20it%20anyway.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20let%20my%20travel%20partner%20plan%20the%20trip%2C%20and%20a%20delayed%20flight%20meant%20that%20all%20his%20plans%20went%20awry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20trip%20cost%20me%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20and%20put%20me%20off%20international%20travel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20seasoned%20traveler%20and%20should%20have%20known%20better%20than%20to%20travel%20during%20the%20holidays%2C%20but%20I%20ignored%20that%20instinct%20%E2%80%94%20and%20paid%20the%20cost.%20My%20ill-fated%20trip%20to%20Morocco%20in%202019%20put%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20of%20my%20romantic%20relationship%20and%20a%20nasty%20dent%20in%20my%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20left%20with%20an%20angry%20ex%2C%20travel%20vouchers%20in%20lieu%20of%20reimbursements%20that%20I%20couldn't%20use%20for%20years%20because%20of%20a%20pandemic%2C%20and%20so%20much%20time%20and%20money%20lost%20that%20I%20refuse%20to%20do%20the%20math.%20Here's%20where%20it%20all%20went%20wrong%20and%20why%20I%20have%20no%20big%20travel%20plans%20on%20the%20horizon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbb13e93-8bba-40fa-8b72-af36755344c3%5C%22%3EOur%20outbound%20flight%20was%20delayed%2C%20delayed%2C%20and%20finally%20canceled%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20first%20day%20of%20my%20very%20limited%20vacation%20at%20the%20airport%20in%20Montreal%3B%20%3Cem%3Emerveilleux%3C%2Fem%3E.%20When%20the%20airline%20finally%20canceled%20the%20flight%20at%201%20a.m.%20and%20sent%20us%20to%20collect%20our%20checked%20luggage%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20make%20lemonade%20from%20the%20lemons%20life%20had%20given%20me%20by%20heading%20into%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20flagged%20down%20an%20airline%20representative%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20book%20my%20own%20hotel%20and%20taxi%2C%20instead%20of%20staying%20near%20the%20airport%20using%20the%20airline%20vouchers.%20The%20rep%20assured%20me%20I'd%20get%20reimbursed%20for%20the%20expenses.%20I%20booked%20a%20nice%20hotel%20in%20the%20Old%20Port%2C%20hailed%20a%20taxi%2C%20and%20off%20we%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20made%20plans%20to%20go%20to%20my%20favorite%20spa%20the%20next%20day%20since%20we%20had%20a%20full%2024%20hours%20until%20our%20rebooked%20flight%20to%20Morocco%3B%20more%20lemonade%2C%20please.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20though%2C%20only%20a%20percentage%20of%20the%20hotel%20and%20taxi%20expenses%20were%20reimbursed%20by%20the%20airline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238509dc3-4e5f-477c-9461-0db01c630592%5C%22%3EI%20let%20my%20man%20friend%20do%20most%20of%20the%20planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20experienced%20traveler%20and%20an%20expert%20planner%2C%20but%20on%20this%20occasion%2C%20I%20let%20go%20of%20the%20reins%20and%20let%20my%20seasoned%20travel%20partner%20take%20the%20lead.%20To%20my%20horror%2C%20he%20planned%20a%20jam-packed%20trip%20that%20had%20us%20moving%20from%20place%20to%20place%20each%20day%20and%20spending%20most%20of%20the%20trip%20en%20route%20in%20a%20black%20Mercedes%20van%20with%20tinted%20windows%2C%20crisscrossing%20the%20Sahara%20Desert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20impossibly%20brisk%20pace%20of%20the%20trip%20and%20the%20time%20difference%20meant%20that%20our%20canceled%20flight%20resulted%20in%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20lost%20on%20canceled%20hotels%2C%20tours%2C%20and%20transportation.%20We%20had%20split%20those%20expenses%20equally%2C%20and%20without%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftravel-insurance%2Fbest-international-travel-insurance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20travel%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20was%20money%20we'd%20never%20get%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20travel%2C%20I%20don't%20like%20being%20told%20when%20and%20where%20to%20go%20and%20what%20to%20look%20at.%20Guided%20group%20tours%20are%20a%20no-go%20for%20me.%20I%20deeply%20value%20my%20freedom%20and%2C%20on%20this%20trip%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20kidnapped%20woman.%20I%20was%20even%20repeatedly%20called%20by%20my%20travel%20partner's%20last%20name.%20As%20a%20widow%20who%20still%20carries%20her%20late%20husband's%20name%2C%20this%20was%20the%20straw%20that%20broke%20the%20camel's%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOh%2C%20and%20I%20rode%20a%20camel%20in%20the%20desert.%20I%20hated%20it.%20My%20camel%20got%20separated%20from%20the%20others%20and%20went%20rogue%2C%20riding%20(slowly)%20into%20the%20sunrise.%20I%20felt%20like%20a%20silly%2C%20privileged%20white%20woman%2C%20buying%20and%20collecting%20experiences%20in%20a%20foreign%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c80d9e4-cec1-4760-84e4-fd8cd2220f7f%5C%22%3EWe%20got%20caught%20in%20tourist%20traps%20everywhere%20we%20went%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20stay%20in%20an%20Airbnb%20or%20apartment%20when%20I%20travel%20so%20that%20I%20can%20cook%2C%20go%20to%20the%20market%20or%20grocery%20store%2C%20save%20a%20little%20money%2C%20eat%20healthy%2C%20and%20do%20as%20the%20locals%20do.%20I%20walk%2C%20bike%2C%20or%20take%20public%20transit.%20I%20plan%20a%20few%20things%20but%20leave%20lots%20of%20space%20to%20change%20my%20mind%2C%20spend%20hours%20reading%20in%20a%20park%2C%20people-watching%20at%20a%20caf%C3%A9%2C%20and%20see%20where%20the%20day%20takes%20me.%20Because%20my%20man%20friend%20had%20hired%20a%20driver%20and%20we%20were%20on%20the%20go%20all%20the%20time%2C%20we%20were%20repeatedly%20delivered%20to%20one%20tourist%20trap%20after%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20driver%20brought%20us%20to%20gift%20shops%20where%20he%20knew%20the%20owner%20and%20pushed%20us%20to%20buy%20things.%20Again%2C%20not%20how%20I%20travel.%20My%20man%20friend%2C%20however%2C%20had%20brought%20two%20large%20suitcases%20on%20our%20trip%3A%20one%20for%20his%20belongings%2C%20and%20the%20other%20for%20the%20things%20he%20was%20going%20to%20buy.%20And%20buy%20he%20did%20%E2%80%94%20rugs%2C%20spices%2C%20knickknacks%2C%20ornaments%2C%20and%20more.%20He%20filled%20that%20suitcase%20with%20souvenirs%20he%20delighted%20at%20haggling%20for.%20I%20paid%20full%20price%20for%20a%20leather%20purse%2C%20which%20irritated%20my%20travel%20partner%2C%20but%20after%20seeing%20a%207-year-old%20boy%20seated%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20outdoor%20market%20sewing%20other%20purses%20just%20like%20it%2C%20I%20didn't%20feel%20like%20haggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20turbulent%20flight%20home%20(literally%20and%20metaphorically)%20I%20vowed%20to%20hit%20pause%20on%20all%20international%20travel.%20As%20this%20was%20December%202019%2C%20I%20got%20my%20wish.%20I%20landed%20safely%20in%20Toronto%20just%20days%20before%202020%20began.%20I%20left%20Morocco%20poorer%2C%20newly%20single%2C%20and%20relieved%20to%20be%20home.%20The%20silver%20lining%3F%20My%20floundering%20relationship%20and%20decadeslong%20wanderlust%20came%20to%20a%20screeching%20halt%20just%20in%20time%20for%20quarantine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20f