they%20spend%20most%20of%20their%20lives.%20These%20turtles%20are%20found%20predominantly%20in%20the%20warm%20waters%20of%20the%20Pacific%2C%20Atlantic%2C%20and%20Indian%20Oceans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20widespread%20presence%2C%20the%20IUCN%20Red%20List%20classifies%20them%20as%20vulnerable%20due%20to%20various%20threats.%20Their%20unique%20mass%20nesting%20behaviour%2C%20Arribada%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E(meaning%20%E2%80%98to%20arrive%E2%80%99%20in%20Spanish)%2C%20is%20a%20rare%20sight%2C%20observed%20in%20only%20a%20few%20locations%20globally%2C%20making%20Odisha%20a%20crucial%20habitat%20for%20their%20survival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20laying%20100%20eggs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turtles%E2%80%99%20journey%20to%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20shores%20is%20a%20remarkable%20display%20of%20natural%20instinct.%20After%20spending%20their%20lives%20roaming%20the%20open%20ocean%2C%20these%20marine%20reptiles%20return%20to%20the%20very%20beaches%20where%20they%20hatched%2C%20driven%20by%20an%20innate%20desire%20to%20perpetuate%20their%20species.%20The%20mating%20process%20occurs%20offshore%2C%20with%20males%20and%20females%20engaging%20in%20courtship%20rituals%20before%20the%20females%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20sandy%20shores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arribada%20is%20a%20synchronised%20nesting%20event%20in%20which%20thousands%20of%20females%20arrive%20simultaneously%20over%20a%20few%20nights.%20This%20synchronisation%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20a%20survival%20strategy%2C%20as%20the%20sheer%20numbers%20of%20females%20overwhelm%20predators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5